# Product Backlog â€“ Library System

## User Stories

As a librarian, I want to add new books, so that users can borrow them.

As a librarian, I want to remove books, so that outdated books are deleted.

As a user, I want to search for books, so that I can find what I need.

As a user, I want to borrow a book, so that I can read it.

As a user, I want to return a book, so that it becomes available again.

As an admin, I want to manage users, so that access is controlled.
